This repository contains tooling, documentation, and smart contract source for the
TROPTIONS / Newpoint Statutory Trust (NST) 700M USD collateral governance and
reserve attestation system (UCC-1 pledge structure).

**Important**: The on-chain components (contracts, attestations) and this tooling
are for governance, evidence, and audit purposes only. The legal authority and
perfected security interest reside in the executed pledge agreement, CIS, and
subsequent UCC filings (source documents in controlled operator storage). All
deployments, attestations, and reliance are subject to legal review, security
audit, and explicit human approvals per the sovereign control plane process.

See README.md, the static review site (site/), and the pledge PDFs for full
context, disclaimers, and the 700M USD cash pledge details (Troptions as secured
party, NST as pledgor, Scotia Bank Canada custody).